[section#thread.lock.unique.cons
    [:en] Constructors, destructor, and assignment
    [:zh_CN] 构造函数，析构函数和赋值
]

[%@lib@ctor unique_lock]
[codeblock:declaration]
unique_lock() noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:ensures]
[:en] [`pm == nullptr] and [`owns == false].
[:zh_CN] [`pm == nullptr] 且 [`owns == false]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor unique_lock]
[codeblock:declaration]
explicit unique_lock(mutex_type& m);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Calls [`m.lock()].
[:zh_CN] 调用 [`m.lock()]。

[para:ensures]
[:en] [`pm == addressof(m)] and [`owns == true].
[:zh_CN] [`pm == addressof(m)] 且 [`owns == true]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor unique_lock]
[codeblock:declaration]
unique_lock(mutex_type& m, defer_lock_t) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:ensures]
[:en] [`pm == addressof(m)] and [`owns == false].
[:zh_CN] [`pm == addressof(m)] 且 [`owns == false]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor unique_lock]
[codeblock:declaration]
unique_lock(mutex_type& m, try_to_lock_t);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:expects]
[:en] The supplied [`Mutex] type meets the [^:oc Lockable] requirements ([#thread.req.lockable.req]).
[:zh_CN] 所提供的 [`Mutex] 类型满足 [^:oc Lockable] 规定（[#thread.req.lockable.req]）。

[para:effects]
[:en] Calls [`m.try_lock()].
[:zh_CN] 调用 [`m.try_lock()]。

[para:ensures]
[:en] [`pm == addressof(m)] and [`owns == res], where [`res] is the value
returned by the call to [`m.try_lock()].
[:zh_CN] [`pm == addressof(m)] 且 [`owns == res]，其中 [`res] 是对
[`m.try_lock()] 的调用所返回的值。
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor unique_lock]
[codeblock:declaration]
unique_lock(mutex_type& m, adopt_lock_t);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:expects]
[:en] The calling thread holds a non-shared lock on [`m].
[:zh_CN] 调用方线程持有 [`m] 上的一个非共享锁。

[para:ensures]
[:en] [`pm == addressof(m)] and [`owns == true].
[:zh_CN] [`pm == addressof(m)] 且 [`owns == true]。

[para:throws]
[:en] Nothing.
[:zh_CN] 无。
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor unique_lock]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class Clock, class Duration>
  unique_lock(mutex_type& m, const chrono::time_point<Clock, Duration>& abs_time);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:expects]
[:en] The supplied [`Mutex] type meets the [^:oc TimedLockable] requirements ([#thread.req.lockable.timed]).
[:zh_CN] 所提供的 [`Mutex] 类型满足 [^:oc TimedLockable] 规定（[#thread.req.lockable.timed]）。

[para:effects]
[:en] Calls [`m.try_lock_until(abs_time)].
[:zh_CN] 调用 [`m.try_lock_until(abs_time)]。

[para:ensures]
[:en] [`pm == addressof(m)] and [`owns == res], where [`res] is the value
returned by the call to [`m.try_lock_until(abs_time)].
[:zh_CN] [`pm == addressof(m)] 且 [`owns == res]，其中 [`res] 是对
[`m.try_lock_until(abs_time)] 的调用所返回的值。
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor unique_lock]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class Rep, class Period>
  unique_lock(mutex_type& m, const chrono::duration<Rep, Period>& rel_time);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:expects]
[:en] The supplied [`Mutex] type meets the [^:oc TimedLockable] requirements ([#thread.req.lockable.timed]).
[:zh_CN] 所提供的 [`Mutex] 类型满足 [^:oc TimedLockable] 规定（[#thread.req.lockable.timed]）。

[para:effects]
[:en] Calls [`m.try_lock_for(rel_time)].
[:zh_CN] 调用 [`m.try_lock_for(rel_time)]。

[para:ensures]
[:en] [`pm == addressof(m)] and [`owns == res], where [`res] is the value
returned by the call to [`m.try_lock_for(rel_time)].
[:zh_CN] [`pm == addressof(m)] 且 [`owns == res]，其中 [`res] 是对
[`m.try_lock_for(rel_time)] 的调用所返回的值。
[div:end]

[%@lib@ctor unique_lock]
[codeblock:declaration]
unique_lock(unique_lock&& u) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:ensures]
[:en] [`pm == u_p.pm] and [`owns == u_p.owns] (where [`u_p] is the state of [`u]
just prior to this construction), [`u.pm == 0] and [`u.owns == false].
[:zh_CN] [`pm == u_p.pm] 且 [`owns == u_p.owns]（其中 [`u_p] 为 [`u] 紧跟这次
构造之前的状态），[`u.pm == 0]，且 [`u.owns == false]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member operator=[!unique_lock]]
[codeblock:declaration]
unique_lock& operator=(unique_lock&& u) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Equivalent to: [`unique_lock(std::move(u)).swap(*this)]
[:zh_CN] 等价于：[`unique_lock(std::move(u)).swap(*this)]

[para:returns]
[:en] [`*this].
[:zh_CN] [`*this]。
[div:end]

[%@lib@dtor unique_lock]
[codeblock:declaration]
~unique_lock();
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] If [`owns] calls [`pm->unlock()].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`owns] 则调用 [`pm->unlock()]。
[div:end]
